                        <p>  As for me and Peter, well, Tropical Chinese closed down this past December due to 62 health violations. Traditions don’t always last forever, so it’s always a perfect time to begin a new one. </p>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p><em>Grant Besner is a Trinity Sophomore who one day aspires to operate his own alpaca farm. His column, “you said duty,” usually runs on alternate Thursdays.</em></p>
